# .gitignore Template for .NET, ASP.NET Core, and Frontend Projects
#
# This .gitignore template is designed for projects using Visual Studio, Rider, Visual Studio Code,
# ASP.NET Core, Blazor, Node.js, and other common development tools. It ignores temporary files,
# build outputs, user-specific settings, and sensitive configuration files to keep your repository clean.
# Suitable for sharing on GitHub Gist and reusing across multiple projects.
#
# Last updated: April 17, 2025

